coming down the mountain.

299
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:19,470
Go to...

300
00:16:20,950 --> 00:16:21,520
You two

301
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,640
go and get

302
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,310
that mischievous girl back.

303
00:16:23,310 --> 00:16:24,710
Don't come back without her!

304
00:16:24,710 --> 00:16:25,040
Yes.

305
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:26,070
Hurry up!

306
00:16:27,310 --> 00:16:28,640
Tie her up if you have to!

307
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:30,190
Didn't I ask you to keep an eye on her?

308
00:16:30,310 --> 00:16:31,590
How could you let her
go down the mountain?

309
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,040
She's never left the Qingyuan Sect.

310
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:35,550
I don't want to lose her.

311
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:36,880
For God's sake,

312
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,160
