and practice partners. We even have to act.

315
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,550
We're like the most filial spirits.

316
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,670
If you hadn't told us
not to hit or scold her,

317
00:16:44,830 --> 00:16:46,070
