beyond measure.

318
00:16:46,190 --> 00:16:48,430
Now she ran away, and you're blaming us.

319
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:50,710
Just let others take care of
that troublesome girl.

320
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:51,640
All right.

321
00:16:51,710 --> 00:16:53,000
Now is not the time for this.

322
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,120
Just go and find her.

323
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,160
Hurry up, will you?

324
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:56,550
Just go.

325
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,600
(I've finally found the lotus seed.)

326
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,470
(I need to send it back now.)

327
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:33,710
