the school of cultivation.

334
00:18:46,990 --> 00:18:49,030
But ever since you released
the news about the lotus seed,

335
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,320
he's the only one

336
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,990
who has taken it from you.

337
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:55,400
The Seven-Leaf Lotus has been lost
for over a hundred years,

338
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:57,080
and there have been no clues.

339
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:01,920
The guardian is looking for it.

340
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,400
Why shouldn't I?

341
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,880
You mean, he is...

342
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:20,600
[Xinhuai Village]

343
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,320
We're finally arrived.

344
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,950
Xueyi, go back with Uncle Centipede.

345
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,080
We should wait for you.

346
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,510
You can't fly with a sword.

347
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:37,710
It will take you a long time

348
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:39,400
