349
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,710
After I complete the challenges,

350
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,510
I'll be much more powerful.

351
00:19:43,670 --> 00:19:46,510
By then, flying with a sword
will be a piece of cake.

352
00:19:46,670 --> 00:19:48,640
I better stay here with you.

353
