to capture me will find me soon.

357
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:56,270
Do you still remember coo-coo-coo?

358
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:57,360
Coo,

359
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,320
coo-coo-coo-coo-coo,

360
00:19:58,470 --> 00:19:58,880
coo-coo.

361
00:19:58,990 --> 00:20:00,270
Each one is different.

362
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,880
Okay, I get it.

363
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:02,800
Just go back.

364
00:20:03,430 --> 00:20:03,880
Okay.

365
00:20:06,710 --> 00:20:08,920
This is the air down the mountain.

366
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,880
Wait for me.

367
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:22,320
Take a look.

368
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:29,670
Good day.

369
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:37,640
Hello, Miss.

370
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:38,470
Welcome.

371
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,400
What would you like to eat?

372
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,710
What are you looking at?

373
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,990
Beautiful.

374
00:20:51,270 --> 00:20:51,840
Beautiful?

375
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:53,120
Do you want it?

376
00:20:53,950 --> 00:20:54,840
Yes.

377
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,950
Obviously, you're not from my village.

378
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:57,880
Sit down.

379
00:21:01,080 --> 00:21:03,320
There's a locust tree spirit
in the Liu family's old house.

380
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:05,230
Whenever he sees someone
with a masculine aura,

381
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:06,600
he beats them up,
dresses them in women's clothes,

382
00:21:06,710 --> 00:21:08,120
and throw them out.

383
00:21:08,230 --> 00:21:09,600
We are afraid of getting beaten up,

384
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:11,750
so we have to dress up like this.

385
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:15,120
The locust tree spirit
is quite interesting.

386
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:18,670
What's interesting about
a perverted locust tree spirit?

387
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,840
What do you want to eat?

388
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:20,840
Make your order.

389
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:21,720
[Menu]

390
00:21:28,080 --> 00:21:29,080
Well,

391
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:34,230
