397
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:48,270
It's a superb delicacy

398
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:49,880
with a rich and savory broth.

399
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:51,750
The noodles are chewy.

400
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:55,080
There is also the special stinky tofu.

401
00:21:57,600 --> 00:21:58,190
Not ten taels,

402
00:21:58,320 --> 00:21:59,080
not five taels,

403
00:21:59,190 --> 00:22:00,640
