404
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:03,400
Well, Miss, would you like to try it?

405
00:22:08,470 --> 00:22:09,710
Not the combo.

406
00:22:10,230 --> 00:22:11,080
How much for a bowl of noodles?

407
00:22:11,430 --> 00:22:11,920
Four maces.

408
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:12,750
Without meat?

409
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:13,430
Three maces.

410
00:22:13,710 --> 00:22:14,400
Just the broth?

411
00:22:14,470 --> 00:22:14,950
One mace.

412
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:15,600
And the noodle soup?

413
00:22:16,470 --> 00:22:16,840
It's free.

414
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:17,560
You...

415
00:22:17,670 --> 00:22:18,270
Are you gonna order or not?

416
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:18,640
Yes.

417
00:22:19,270 --> 00:22:20,270
What's your order?

418
00:22:22,190 --> 00:22:24,230
I'll have a bowl of noodle soup.

419
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:28,880
Boss!

420
00:22:29,320 --> 00:22:30,270
Don't come to a restaurant
with no money.

421
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:32,270
If you can't afford it, just get lost!

422
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,360
Do you know who you're throwing out?

423
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:37,990
You know what,

424
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:39,470
after I catch the spirit,

425
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:41,230
I won't eat here even if you beg me to.

426
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:42,750
Help!

427
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:43,400
Stop!

428
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:43,950
Help!

429
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:44,800
Stop!

430
00:22:44,990 --> 00:22:45,710
Don't run! Stop!

431
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,400
Help!

432
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:49,320
Stop!

433
00:22:50,430 --> 00:22:51,030
Stop!

434
00:22:51,030 --> 00:22:51,750
- Help!
- Stop!

435
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:52,920
Stop!

436
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:54,320
Don't run!

437
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:55,120
Catch him!

438
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:58,400
They're abducting a man.

439
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:01,070
Is the world down the mountain
so interesting?

440
00:23:01,470 --> 00:23:03,510
It's different from
what's written in books.

441
00:23:03,990 --> 00:23:05,070
Help!

442
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,120
Don't run!

443
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:07,070
Stop!

444
00:23:07,230 --> 00:23:07,470
Help!

445
00:23:07,470 --> 00:23:08,070
Don't run!

446
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:10,840
Brother!

447
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:12,440
Come back!

448
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:17,790
This one is better.

449
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,030
Don't worry, sister.

450
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:21,120
We'll take care of
your lifelong happiness.

451
00:23:21,470 --> 00:23:23,550
You can have anyone you want.

452
00:23:24,990 --> 00:23:26,070
Are you serious, dude?

453
00:23:27,990 --> 00:23:28,470
How audacious!

454
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:30,160
How dare you abduct a man

455
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:32,310
in public?

456
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:38,710
Don't be afraid.

457
00:23:40,840 --> 00:23:43,750
Listen, since I'm here today,

458
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:44,920
I'd like to see who dares to touch him.

459
00:23:45,030 --> 00:23:46,840
Are you teaching me how to do things?

460
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,360
I'm teaching you how to be a human being.

461
00:23:48,710 --> 00:23:49,510
Get her!

462
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,120
Go!

463
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:16,840
Senior, I've won this time.

464
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,790
I only read about

465
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,310
the Farmer and the Viper story in books.

466
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:09,030
Today I'm experiencing it.

467
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,400
I helped you out of kindness,

468
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,400
but you returned the favor
by molesting me.

469
00:25:14,120 --> 00:25:14,640
Sorry.

470
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:15,470
You...

471
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,310
Don't think you can do whatever you want

472
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:19,400
just because you're handsome.

473
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:21,750
Qingyuan is the most prestigious sect
of cultivators,

474
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:24,990
and I'm the inner disciple
of its leader.

475
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,310
How dare you mess with me?

476
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,440
Do you still hate me?

477
00:25:32,230 --> 00:25:33,990
What's wrong with you?

478
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:36,310
You know what,

479
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:39,270
I have something to do now,
so we're square.

480
00:25:39,790 --> 00:25:41,750
You have a flower on your head,
you fraud.

481
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:43,790
Where are you going?

482
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,680
As a heroine like me,

483
00:25:47,990 --> 00:25:49,750
I'm off to do good deeds.

484
00:25:49,990 --> 00:25:50,680
Let go of me.

485
00:25:52,270 --> 00:25:55,120
No, I won't let you leave me again.

486
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:58,270
(She doesn't remember me.)

487
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:00,600
I see.

488
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:01,960
You're trying to extort me.

489
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:02,840
No way.

490
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:04,750
You've hurt my arm.

491
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,270
Are you just gonna walk away?

492
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,960
You should be responsible for me.

493
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,790
Let me see if I really hurt your arm

494
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,710
with my sword.

495
00:26:15,990 --> 00:26:16,880
Don't scream.

496
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:31,200
It's a fairly rare mutant spirit root.

497
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,270
He doesn't have spiritual power yet.

498
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:38,030
He has a prodigious talent
for cultivation.

499
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:39,510
(With Lian Wen's level of cultivation,)

500
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,840
(there is no way
she can't feel my spiritual power.)

501
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,680
(Could it be...)

502
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,360
Are you done touching me?

503
00:26:56,710 --> 00:26:58,160
(If I had known
I would take him as my disciple,)

504
00:26:58,360 --> 00:26:59,640
(I wouldn't have hurt him.)

505
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,440
(What do I do now?)

506
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:06,030
What are you going to do?

507
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,440
I'll be responsible for you.

508
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,070
How?

509
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,310
By marrying you.

510
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:12,030
You definitely don't want what.

511
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:15,120
How about this,

512
00:27:15,990 --> 00:27:18,230
I'll take you as my disciple.

513
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:22,600
How's that?

514
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:26,440
Do you feel really lucky now?

515
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:28,550
I've longed to become a cultivator,

516
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:31,680
but it's a big deal to take on a master.

517
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:33,470
Isn't this too hasty?

518
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:37,510
Alright, I happen to have
an important task

519
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,400
that can prove it to you.

520
00:27:43,310 --> 00:27:46,400
Do you know there's a locust tree spirit
in this village?

521
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:48,750
A locust tree spirit?

522
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:50,960
A locust tree spirit.

523
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:52,960
It's scary.

524
00:27:53,230 --> 00:27:54,880
I'm just passing by.
I don't know anything.

525
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,510
I came down from the mountain

526
00:28:00,750 --> 00:28:02,160
for this important task,

527
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:05,840
to subdue the locust tree spirit
and protect the people.

528
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,960
I'll let you follow me

529
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:12,510
and show you my strength,

530
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:14,640
which you can't even imagine.

531
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:15,600
Really?

532
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:19,230
That's great. I'd love to see it.

533
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,200
Let's go.

534
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:22,400
Okay, let's go.

535
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:23,360
Come on.

536
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,750
Hold on.

537
00:28:28,510 --> 00:28:29,470
What's your name?

538
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:30,960
Cui Chen.

539
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:47,840
Looks like this is the place.

540
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:49,750
My future disciple.

541
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:51,550
Don't be afraid.

542
00:28:51,790 --> 00:28:52,990
Stay close to me.

543
00:28:53,230 --> 00:28:56,070
I will protect you with my life.

544
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:57,790
Yes.

545
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:00,160
Well, I'm powerless.

546
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,160
I have to count on you.

547
00:29:02,270 --> 00:29:04,230
No problem.

548
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:05,510
Leave it to me.

549
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:11,310
(Zhao Tantan, what are you afraid of?)

550
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,750
(You've been domineering)

551
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:14,470
(in the den of monsters
since you were a kid.)

552
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:16,680
(What's a mere locust tree spirit
to you?)

553
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:19,880
I'll show you what I'm capable of.

554
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,990
What are you doing here?

555
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,510
I was wondering

556
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,400
why I could smell something foul
from miles away.

557
00:29:34,840 --> 00:29:35,960
Turns out

558
00:29:36,070 --> 00:29:37,680
it's the poor Qingyuan Sect.

559
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,120
Why don't you hide in the mountains?

560
00:29:40,230 --> 00:29:41,600
You got some nerve to come here.

561
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:45,960
His breath is quite bad.
Can you smell it?

562
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,230
It is quite bad.

563
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:51,960
We're here to eliminate the evil spirits

564
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,200
and bring peace to the people.

565
00:29:53,470 --> 00:29:55,640
You two? Eliminate the evil spirits?

566
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:56,640
How ridiculous.

567
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:01,920
As for us, we were specially invited

568
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:03,990
by the village chief
from the Tianyin Palace.

569
00:30:04,230 --> 00:30:06,230
If you're smart, get lost now,

570
00:30:06,550 --> 00:30:08,600
in case you should be scared

571
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,120
by my force.

572
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:11,600
Sir.

573
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,680
Go back and prepare the money.

574
00:30:13,790 --> 00:30:15,790
We'll take care of this for you.

575
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:16,440
Okay.

576
00:30:17,710 --> 00:30:20,990
Don't you know the chief came to us first?

577
00:30:20,990 --> 00:30:22,310
The capable one gets the job.

578
00:30:40,360 --> 00:30:42,470
My goodness.

579
00:30:46,030 --> 00:30:48,200
Oh, my God. It's cruel.

580
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:52,920
I told you

581
00:30:53,270 --> 00:30:54,840
this is what happens

582
00:30:54,990 --> 00:30:57,160
when you're not strong enough.

583
00:30:57,840 --> 00:30:59,790
But I'm different.

584
00:31:00,030 --> 00:31:02,840
Even the thousand-year crab spirit
is no match for me.

585
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,440
I'm not afraid of animals,

586
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,600
let alone a plant.

587
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,030
Sure.

588
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,270
(I can't let him find out)

589
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,680
(that I haven't built my foundation
and I can't fly.)

590
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:16,990
Look, the people from the Tianyin Palace

591
00:31:16,990 --> 00:31:18,600
are so cowardly.

592
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,200
They only dare to fly in.

593
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:23,030
But for us,
who are from a prestigious sect,

594
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,790
we must enter through the front gate.

595
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:39,030
This locust tree spirit is
quite powerful.

596
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:41,550
The door is sealed
with some powerful spells.

597
00:31:42,070 --> 00:31:44,070
In order not to alarm the spirit,

598
00:31:44,710 --> 00:31:46,400
I've decided to take the smart way.

599
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:48,990
I'll climb the wall.

600
00:31:57,030 --> 00:31:57,550
Well,

601
00:31:57,710 --> 00:31:59,270
since you haven't joined
our Qingyuan Sect,

602
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,160
I can't let you learn my magic skills.

603
00:32:01,470 --> 00:32:03,990
Turn around and don't look back.

604
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:27,230
(Turns out the gate should be pulled,
not pushed.)

605
00:32:27,470 --> 00:32:28,840
(This guy is quite smart.)

606
00:32:34,070 --> 00:32:35,160
This is the tree.

607
00:32:39,070 --> 00:32:41,230
It doesn't seem special at all.

608
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:21,960
Oh, no, what's the next line?

609
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:25,470
How could I forget it at this moment?

610
00:33:30,120 --> 00:33:30,840
Watch out!

